I work as a therapist in addiction and mental health, and I know you are going through a lot right now, and I would like you to know there are places for you to reach out and get the help you need in a confidential manner.  I encourage you to look up some local mental health services and to seek treatment for the disordered eating and substance misuse.  Good luck, you can do it.
